        <template>
            You and me both. Would you ever consider writing mystery novels?
            <oob>
                <robot></robot>
            </oob>
        </template>
    </category>

    <category>
        <pattern>_</pattern>
        <that>Would you ever consider writing mystery novels?</that>
        <template>
            I think you've got a novel in you, especially after all your experience.
